IMAPAccount lucas
Host monday.mxrouting.net 
User lucas@lucashorton.com
PassCmd "pass $(hostnamectl hostname)/EMAIL_PASSWORD"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore lucas-remote
Account lucas 

MaildirStore lucas-local
Path ~/.mail/
Inbox ~/.mail/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel lucas
Far :lucas-remote:
Near :lucas-local:
Patterns * !INBOX/spam
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel lucas-spam
Far :lucas-remote:INBOX/spam
Near :lucas-local:Spam
Create Near
Expunge Both
